PrecisAcceptance of the transfer from the Province of ONTARIO of the administration and control over a waterlot situated on the shores of Fisher Bay on Lake Huron, in the Village of HILTON BEACH, that contains an area of some 5.46 hectares, which will be used to accommodate the expansion of a federal wharf.
